tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ethical_dilemmas (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    dilemma_description TEXT,
    date_encountered TIMESTAMPTZ,
    AI_system VARCHAR,
    resolution VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE ai_feedback (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    dilemma_id INT NOT NULL,
    feedback TEXT NOT NULL,
    feedback_date DATE NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT fk_dilemma_id
        FOREIGN KEY (dilemma_id)
        REFERENCES ethical_dilemmas(id)
);

CREATE TABLE ai_encounters (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ai_system_id INT,
    encounter_date DATE,
    encounter_location TEXT,
    resolution TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (ai_system_id) REFERENCES ai_systems(id)
);

CREATE TABLE ethical_dilemmas (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  dilemma_description TEXT,
  ai_system_involved TEXT,
  date_encountered DATE
)

CREATE TABLE dilemma_images (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  dilemma_id INTEGER REFERENCES ethical_dilemmas(id),
  image_url TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE dilemma_sources (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  dilemma_id INTEGER REFERENCES ethical_dilemmas(id),
  source_name TEXT,
  source_url TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE dilemma_feedback (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  dilemma_id INTEGER REFERENCES ethical_dilemmas(id),
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE dilemma_tags (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  dilemma_id INTEGER REFERENCES ethical_dilemmas(id),
  tag_name TEXT
)
